{"tid":626394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝又3個自殺","createTime":"2018-04-12T05:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T11:09:37.000Z","uid":38671,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"385465108d276371c67910c2ea14995d65465b0e","tid":626394,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n長沙灣深盛道9號宇晴軒1座，清晨5時許，一名姓周29歲女子從高處墮下，倒臥平台，保安員發現報警。救護員到場證實墮樓女子已經死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方在現場沒有撿獲遺書，初步調查女事主從一單位墮下，據了解她有情緒病記錄。警方調查事件無可疑。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180412/58062563\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F58062563&d=Dt7%2BsZKySRTPXTrBALTzW8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=811d4b2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F58062563&h=06814e55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180412/58062563</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n青衣藍澄灣，早上7時29分，一名中年女子從高處墮下，倒臥地上花槽昏迷不醒，其20歲兒子發現報警。救護員到場證實女事主當場死亡。警方經調查後獲悉事主姓黃(50歲)，警方撿獲遺書，初步調查顯示事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍確定。據悉，黃婦有身體病患，不排除她因病厭世尋死。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180412/58062682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F58062682&d=Dt7%2BsZKySRTPXTrBALTzW8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=df9df460\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F58062682&h=8799e5ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180412/58062682</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍田麗港城19座，早上10時左右，一名男子被家人發現上吊自殺。救援人員接報到場將他解下，惟送院後不治。警方正展開調查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180412/58063593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F58063593&d=Dt7%2BsZKySRTPXTrBALTzW8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=380a2c7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F58063593&h=22a6d230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180412/58063593</a>"},{"pid":"654d927a42ec3f1d2647a8fae9709246c55f4a45","tid":626394,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:25:29.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00f2505228b4b8b6535df44fb81129bc8eccc58","tid":626394,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:43:53.000Z","msg":"革命尚未成功，港獨派逃兵，論罪當誅"},{"pid":"d6465cb93395204318e22295d6cd16b64bdf334d","tid":626394,"uid":42407,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"有乜所謂？"},{"pid":"3c113b1f6262d8f608401ac6a657e49506cabc51","tid":626394,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:46:20.000Z","msg":"3/700萬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0.01%都無"},{"pid":"888767783f3163ffb4ea99f4762ecc72960beaf0","tid":626394,"uid":142532,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:47:21.000Z","msg":"私樓撚都要自殺.."},{"pid":"dfee6821996da3dacf4a9c670183ec12abf39727","tid":626394,"uid":95,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a00f2505228b4b8b6535df44fb81129bc8eccc58","tid":626394,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:43:53.000Z","msg":"革命尚未成功，港獨派逃兵，論罪當誅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"乜撚野港獨派呀屌你老母？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a726518bf231cc955d35e30b0e635bc46503d6b9","tid":626394,"uid":75655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20